            "title": "歐股個別發展  法股跑贏",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲主要股市收市表現不一。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市微升0.05%，報614點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">法國CAC指數報8227點，升70點，升幅近0.9%，表現優於其他主要市場。德國DAX指數則報24155點，跌39點，跌幅近0.2%；英國富時100指數報10457點，跌19點，跌幅同樣接近0.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利富時MIB指數收報47907點，升0.26%或121點；西班牙IBEX 35指數收報17885點，跌0.67%或120點。</p>\n</div>",
